- and the Shooting Star.
- This job is really dangerous.

00:53.722 --> 00:55.320
Whoa! Geez!

00:55.355 --> 00:59.108
- Wha... whoa, mama!
- Amethyst!

00:59.192 --> 01:02.363
Don't worry. I'll get you out.

01:04.447 --> 01:07.116
We've got to get
Steven out of here!

01:07.200 --> 01:09.368
I'm sending you back
to the temple.

01:09.419 --> 01:11.453
But, Garnet, how are
you gonna ...

01:11.538 --> 01:13.372
Huh?

01:13.423 --> 01:16.625
