01:34.194 --> 01:38.397
Look at you now, stuck in a bubble.

01:38.398 --> 01:40.149
Hmm.

01:40.233 --> 01:43.402
Let me see if I can...

01:47.914 --> 01:51.293
Yeah!
Wha...? Ugh! Whoa!

01:51.377 --> 01:54.296
Wha!

01:54.380 --> 01:55.881
Whew.
Huh?

01:55.965 --> 01:59.251
